126	dpb7beswm7ga3l6fge6qcaw7	Conveyor Toaster	<p><span style="font-size:22px;"><strong>We have various of type / color for your choosing. Each range have 3 sizes: 1 slice &nbsp;mouth (150 slices/hour), 2 slices mouth (300 slices/hour) &amp; 3 slices mouth (450 slices/hour).</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Excellent Efficiency</strong></span></p><p style="--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;--tw-blur:;--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contain-layout:;--tw-contain-paint:;--tw-contain-size:;--tw-contain-style:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-gradient-from-position:;--tw-gradient-to-position:;--tw-gradient-via-position:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-ring-color:rgba(0,174,239,.5);--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-saturate:;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-sepia:;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:rgb(59, 66, 56);font-family:proxima_nova, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17.6px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;">This conveyor toaster can toast up to 300 slices of bread or bagel halves per hour, letting you keep up with your busiest hours throughout the day. And thanks to its energy-saving standby mode, you can conserve energy when this toaster isn't in use. The standby mode keeps the elements at reduced power to conserve energy between meal periods, but reduces preheat time when going into high-service meal periods.</p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:50%;"><img style="aspect-ratio:799/530;" src="https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Front_Side_0693ca0913.JPG" alt="Front Side.JPG" srcset="https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/thumbnail_Front_Side_0693ca0913.JPG 235w,https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/small_Front_Side_0693ca0913.JPG 500w,https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/medium_Front_Side_0693ca0913.JPG 750w," sizes="100vw" width="799" height="530"></figure><p style="margin-left:0px;"><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Convenient Versatility</strong></span></p><p style="--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;--tw-blur:;--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contain-layout:;--tw-contain-paint:;--tw-contain-size:;--tw-contain-style:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-gradient-from-position:;--tw-gradient-to-position:;--tw-gradient-via-position:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-ring-color:rgba(0,174,239,.5);--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-saturate:;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-sepia:;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:rgb(59, 66, 56);font-family:proxima_nova, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17.6px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;">For versatility, this toaster can dispense product from the front or back on the included chutes. Dispensing the product out of the back allows for pass-through versatility &nbsp;from back of house to front of house, while dispensing the product in the front reduces the countertop footprint of the unit, and even allows users to toast product themselves to reduce labor cost.</p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:50%;"><img style="aspect-ratio:786/544;" src="https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Rear_Side_9168a8524e.jpg" alt="Rear Side.jpg" srcset="https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/thumbnail_Rear_Side_9168a8524e.jpg 225w,https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/small_Rear_Side_9168a8524e.jpg 500w,https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/medium_Rear_Side_9168a8524e.jpg 750w," sizes="100vw" width="786" height="544"></figure><p><span style="font-size:20px;"><strong>Easy to Use</strong></span></p><p style="--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;--tw-blur:;--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contain-layout:;--tw-contain-paint:;--tw-contain-size:;--tw-contain-style:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-gradient-from-position:;--tw-gradient-to-position:;--tw-gradient-via-position:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-ring-color:rgba(0,174,239,.5);--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-saturate:;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-sepia:;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);color:rgb(59, 66, 56);font-family:proxima_nova, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17.6px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;">Different breads toast differently, from white and rye to grainy whole wheat. To adjust the toaster to the perfect setting, use the easy-to-use dial on the front to slow down or speed up the conveyor. The faster it moves, the less toasted the bread will be. This is also great for ensuring that a customer's toast is toasted to their preferred crispiness!</p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:50%;"><img style="aspect-ratio:6720/4480;" src="https://kitchen-utensils.s3.ap-southea