ont-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;">The commercial kitchen is a harsh environment, so this toaster is built accordingly. It's a great workhorse for cafes, buffets, and coffee shops, especially during the morning meal rush! Its stainless steel exterior provides long-lasting durability, while a pull-out crumb tray makes it easy to clean.</p>	0	2025-11-25 08:07:37.346	2025-11-25 09:56:20.685	\N	1	1	en
